| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7235 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0571670e-bc82-5389-aeb9-a349d976db30"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
